caption:
Table 1: GTA5 to Cityscapes, our results are averages from three runs, and shown as per-class IoU and mIoU. We also compare to several 
previous works. We present results for DACS, as well as for training only on data from the source domain.

Table 2: SYNTHIA to Cityscapes, our results are averages from three runs, and shown as per-class IoU and mIoU for 13 and 16 classes. 
We also compare to several previous works.

Table 3: Results from experiments when using Naive Mixing, only using pseudo-labelling and when applying CutMix or CowMix instead 
of the default ClassMix. All experiments are performed on GTA5 ? Cityscapes. For comparison our results from Table 1 are also included.
